For nearly 10 years, @emackeycreates has created content for brands like Remy Martin, Hennessy, Google, Twitter, Toyota, Mercedes, Dove, Essence Magazine and more. Now, he is sharing some of his knowledge and expertise with rising business owners. 
 In this video, he gives the basics of logo design, and also offers logo design services (to small businesses) for only $100! Tag someone that may be interested.

We are creating this network to share the best of Black experiences with the diaspora. ALL content is created by Black Content Creators (filmakers, documentarians, Real Estate, Biblical and Black Diasporic Historians, Finance, Health/Wellness, Lifestyle, Music, Poetic Arts, Family, Clean Eating, etc.) sharing their best with us all.

We are asking that you support this independent Blac media outlet by purchasing a subscription, liking/sharing our IG page, help us get to 500 subscribers within our firts quarter, RECOMMEND Content Creators and suggestions for future programming.

Join us for our Virtual Pre-Launch event, July 28th at 7PM for more information DM or email us at support@sablenetwork.tv

IG: @sablenetworktv

@famjenks @tscllc  @sablenetworktv

@shawntblanchard mentors on how 𝐨𝐧𝐞 𝐬𝐤𝐢𝐥𝐥 can launch multiple streams of impact and income.

More specifically he has mentored hundreds of people on how a book can be a business anchor that can lead to 20 different streams of impact and income!

That’s huge!

Just think about a book that leads to speaking, workshops, curriculum, webinars, merchandise, consultations, etc…

Follow Shawn and learn his methods starting with becoming an impactful author!

Join his free Master Class this Sunday at 7pm EST. Secure your spot ASAP!
